<lb n="0379b23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0379b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0379b2401">總<note n="0379002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">施＝旋ヵ【原】</note><app n="0379002"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">旋</rdg></app>了然後洗手。又施道場中發遣奉送聖
<lb n="0379b25" ed="T"/>眾。收却供養物。然後塗壇。</p>
